169→/// | POST   | `/api/projects/:id/sync-github` | Sync issues from GitHub   |
170→/// | POST   | `/api/projects/:id/issues`      | Create an issue           |
171→/// | GET    | `/api/issues/:id`               | Get issue detail          |
