 17→/// Decision for where to move an issue after pipeline completion.
 18→#[derive(Debug, Clone, PartialEq)]
 19→pub enum PromoteDecision {
 20→    /// Clean run — move to Done.
 21→    Done,
 22→    /// Has warnings or issues — move to InReview.
